<h1 class="firstHeading" id="firstHeading" lang="en">1998–99 UEFA Cup</h1>

<td class="noprint" colspan="2" style="text-align:center">

<div style="float: right;"><a href="/wiki/1999%E2%80%932000_UEFA_Cup" title="1999–2000 UEFA Cup">1999–2000</a> →</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>The <b>1998–99 <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/UEFA_Cup" title="UEFA Cup">UEFA Cup</a></b> was won by <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/Parma_F.C." title="Parma F.C.">Parma</a> comfortably in the final against <a href="/wiki/Olympique_de_Marseille" title="Olympique de Marseille">Marseille</a>. It was their second title in the competition.</p>
<p>It was the last edition of the old format UEFA Cup, before the <a href="/wiki/UEFA_Cup_Winners%27_Cup" title="UEFA Cup Winners' Cup">Cup Winners' Cup</a> was merged into it to include domestic cup winners, and an extra knockout round was added. The new format was last played in the 2003-04 season and was later replaced by a Group Stage format in 2004-05.</p>
<p></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">
<p><span class="summary" style="display: none;"><a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/FK_Baku" title="FK Baku">Dynamo Baku</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Azerbaijan" title="Azerbaijan"><img alt="Azerbaijan" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="1200" height="12" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg/23px-Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg/35px-Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg/46px-Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> v <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Romania" title="Romania"><img alt="Romania" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="400" data-file-width="600" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Romania.svg/23px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Romania.svg/35px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Romania.svg/45px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/FC_Arge%C5%9F_Pite%C5%9Fti" title="FC Argeş Piteşti">Argeş Piteşti</a></span></p>

<th class="vcard attendee" style="width:39%; text-align:right"><span class="fn org"><a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/FK_Baku" title="FK Baku">Dynamo Baku</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Azerbaijan" title="Azerbaijan"><img alt="Azerbaijan" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="1200" height="12" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg/23px-Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg/35px-Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg/46px-Flag_of_Azerbaijan.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span></span></th>
<th style="width:22%; text-align:center">1–2</th>
<th class="vcard attendee" style="width:39%; text-align:left"><span class="fn org"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Romania" title="Romania"><img alt="Romania" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="400" data-file-width="600" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Romania.svg/23px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Romania.svg/35px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Romania.svg/45px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/FC_Arge%C5%9F_Pite%C5%9Fti" title="FC Argeş Piteşti">Argeş Piteşti</a></span></th>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_2">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">
<p><span class="summary" style="display: none;"><a href="/wiki/Red_Star_Belgrade" title="Red Star Belgrade">Red Star Belgrade</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Federal_Republic_of_Yugoslavia" title="Federal Republic of Yugoslavia"><img alt="Federal Republic of Yugoslavia" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="300" data-file-width="600" height="12" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg/23px-Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg/35px-Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg/46px-Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> v <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Russia" title="Russia"><img alt="Russia" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="900" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f3/Flag_of_Russia.svg/23px-Flag_of_Russia.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f3/Flag_of_Russia.svg/35px-Flag_of_Russia.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f3/Flag_of_Russia.svg/45px-Flag_of_Russia.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a href="/wiki/FC_Rotor_Volgograd" title="FC Rotor Volgograd">Rotor Volgograd</a></span></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_2">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">
<p><span class="summary" style="display: none;"><a href="/wiki/FC_Rotor_Volgograd" title="FC Rotor Volgograd">Rotor Volgograd</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Russia" title="Russia"><img alt="Russia" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="900" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f3/Flag_of_Russia.svg/23px-Flag_of_Russia.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f3/Flag_of_Russia.svg/35px-Flag_of_Russia.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f3/Flag_of_Russia.svg/45px-Flag_of_Russia.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> v <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Federal_Republic_of_Yugoslavia" title="Federal Republic of Yugoslavia"><img alt="Federal Republic of Yugoslavia" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="300" data-file-width="600" height="12" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg/23px-Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg/35px-Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg/46px-Flag_of_FR_Yugoslavia.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Red_Star_Belgrade" title="Red Star Belgrade">Red Star Belgrade</a></span></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_3">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_4">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">

<p><i>Abandoned at half-time after official injured by firework, Fiorentina led 2–1 (<a href="/wiki/Lu%C3%ADs_Oliveira" title="Luís Oliveira">Oliveira</a> <img alt="Goal" data-file-height="313" data-file-width="313" height="13" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Soccerball_shade.svg/13px-Soccerball_shade.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Soccerball_shade.svg/20px-Soccerball_shade.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Soccerball_shade.svg/26px-Soccerball_shade.svg.png 2x" title="Goal" width="13"/> <small style="vertical-align: middle;">12'</small>, <small style="vertical-align: middle;">39'</small> – <a href="/wiki/Mats_Gren" title="Mats Gren">Gren</a> <img alt="Goal" data-file-height="313" data-file-width="313" height="13" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Soccerball_shade.svg/13px-Soccerball_shade.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Soccerball_shade.svg/20px-Soccerball_shade.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Soccerball_shade.svg/26px-Soccerball_shade.svg.png 2x" title="Goal" width="13"/> <small style="vertical-align: middle;">31'</small>). Match awarded 0–3 to Grasshopper</i><br/>
<i>Grasshopper won 3–2 on aggregate.</i></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_5">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<div id="Real_Betis_v_Bologna">
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_6">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_7">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div id="Bologna_v_Marseille">
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">
<p><span class="summary" style="display: none;"><a href="/wiki/Bologna_F.C._1909" title="Bologna F.C. 1909">Bologna</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Italy" title="Italy"><img alt="Italy" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="1000" data-file-width="1500" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/03/Flag_of_Italy.svg/23px-Flag_of_Italy.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/03/Flag_of_Italy.svg/35px-Flag_of_Italy.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/03/Flag_of_Italy.svg/45px-Flag_of_Italy.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> v <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/France" title="France"><img alt="France" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="900" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c3/Flag_of_France.svg/23px-Flag_of_France.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c3/Flag_of_France.svg/35px-Flag_of_France.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c3/Flag_of_France.svg/45px-Flag_of_France.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Olympique_de_Marseille" title="Olympique de Marseille">Marseille</a></span></p>

<tr>
<td>
<div style="text-align:right">20 April 1999<br/>
19:30 (<a href="/wiki/Central_European_Time" title="Central European Time">CET</a>)<br/></div>

</tr>
<tr style="vertical-align:top;font-size:85%">

<div style="clear:both;"></div>

<p><i>Bologna 1–1 Marseille on aggregate. Marseille won on away goals.</i></p>

<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Final">Final</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=1998%E2%80%9399_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Final">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
